{"tid":994373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣導演好狂！天安門拍「中華民國萬歲」","createTime":"2019-01-24T15:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T09:27:49.000Z","uid":5195,"like":602,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"3acc02667252a62f4233af113f871cad05dc681c","tid":994373,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T15:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tYfJ7t0aV6rESI4MstbcAA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDUw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/b8a9725a031189eac7ebb6d6ef9adb3e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FtYfJ7t0aV6rESI4MstbcAA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDUw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fb8a9725a031189eac7ebb6d6ef9adb3e&h=e52ddaf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n堪稱史上最強「政治借位」讓網友讚好狂！有台灣團隊日前應中國「網易雲音樂盛典」邀請前往北京拍片，並由台灣導演擔任總執導，該名導演在天安門廣場拍照時發揮巧思，借位拍出「中華民國萬歲」，但照片曝光立馬引發中國網民不滿怒喊肉搜！<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，中國《網易》旗下的《網易雲音樂》20日邀請台灣導演赴北京拍片，該名導演在天安門廣場背對牆上原本寫有「中華人民共和國萬歲」大字，用頭手巧妙遮住「人」與「共和」後拍下「中華民國萬歲」。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，《網易雲音樂》得知後已終止與台灣團隊合作，中國網民們紛痛批「耍這種小聰明，估計以後沒機會來撈錢了」、「煽動對立，製造仇恨」，但也有人稱讚「很有創意啊」、「超有膽量的」，至於台灣鄉民則笑稱「終於有藍綠共識惹」、「完美詮釋一中各表」，也有人譏「習大大恐氣到把匾額拆囉XD」。"},{"pid":"8cc540deb4e685a59a7786423e9df5cae5984e1e","tid":994373,"uid":86828,"like":204,"dislike":4,"score":200,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T15:47:40.000Z","msg":"撚狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dcda822a981fae9afc912c9f28a852a67f8cbb7","tid":994373,"uid":810,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T15:48:54.000Z","msg":"蟈網民: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105117275dbd701a6fd5e3f3d990f4c779e8cd4c","tid":9